{"tid":2458093,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「奉先論股」 三十六計之一 「瞞天過海」","createTime":"2021-03-23T07:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T14:52:44.000Z","uid":149018,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"40dd5a1961520a1d2d887afb4f89af0f23913947","tid":2458093,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"「用兵如孫子，策謀三十六。」<br />\n溫侯先論三十六，後論孫子兵法。<br />\n<br />\n三十六計 - 第一計<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">瞞天過海</span></span><br />\n備周而意怠，常見則不疑，陰在陽之內，不在陽之對。太陽，太陰。<br />\n<br />\n奉先譯：散戶總認為選股事前功夫準備周全，就容易鬆懈 ; 平時看慣了的財報、新聞來源，就往往不在懷疑了，秘計隱藏於暴露的事物中，而不是和公開的形式相排斥。非常公開的往往蘊藏着非常機密的。所以買賣股票需有獨立思考，財經資訊有時候逆向思考或會有意外得著。<br />\n<br />\n奉先獻醜，將和大家定期一起學習三十六計用之於市場中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFx8iqa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFx8iqa.png&h=3e7cbc6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85d8d41ccf281ddc76af01b4414bb7f83ac98a21","tid":2458093,"uid":13731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:18:00.000Z","msg":"做乜撚<br />\n智力-100"},{"pid":"25a38ae6a589c396e2727e129411fe3c5b6d3a7d","tid":2458093,"uid":379710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"將軍英明，未將誓死跟隨將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c54d0f34401f556fcba9ce0506e1e8d1e8eaf8","tid":2458093,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85d8d41ccf281ddc76af01b4414bb7f83ac98a21","tid":2458093,"uid":13731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:18:00.000Z","msg":"做乜撚<br />\n智力-100"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:29:32.000Z","msg":"以計論股，以奇制勝"},{"pid":"8b3c0558affa6f1639dff78882553a2e5f9faa66","tid":2458093,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"論今日Sqqq可行性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d020873121c5f4ce32968b615e2004813d3e3291","tid":245809